OL,7,FA 70-year-old woman has admitted
OL,8,Fcausing the death by dangerous driving
OL,9,Fof a baby girl who was hit by a car
OL,10,Foutside a hospital.
OL,12,FBridget Carole Curtis, of Begelly,
OL,13,Fappeared at Swansea Crown Court on
OL,14,FFriday, 20 September, where she
OL,15,Fadmitted the charge relating to the
OL,16,Fdeath of eight-month-old Mabli Cariad
OL,17,FHall.
