OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FMabli died from severe traumatic brain
OL,8,Finjuries after being struck by a white
OL,9,FBMW car while in her pram at the front
OL,10,Fentrance of Withybush Hospital in
OL,11,FHaverfordwest, Pembrokeshire, on June
OL,12,F21, 2023.
OL,14,FShe was airlifted to the University
OL,15,FHospital of Wales in Cardiff and later
OL,16,Ftransferred to Bristol Royal Hospital
OL,17,Ffor Children, where she died in the
OL,18,Fearly hours of June 25.
