OL,7,FJudge Geraint Walters released Curtis
OL,8,Fon unconditional bail ahead of her
OL,9,Fsentencing hearing at Swansea Crown
OL,10,FCourt on November 22.
OL,12,FThe judge disqualified Curtis from
OL,13,Fdriving and said psychiatric and pre-
OL,14,Fsentence reports would take place
OL,15,Fbefore the hearing.
OL,17,FHe told her: "You will probably have
OL,18,Funderstood already that the granting
OL,19,Fof bail and the asking of reports
OL,20,Fcan't carry any indication of the
OL,21,Fsentence that could be passed upon you.
