OL,7,F"You can have your bail until the day
OL,8,Fof sentence."
OL,10,FJohn Dye, representing Curtis, said
OL,11,Fhis client was 70 years old and had a
OL,12,Ffull, clean driving licence and no
OL,13,Fprevious convictions.
OL,15,FHe told the court: "She is absolutely
OL,16,Fdevastated to be here."
OL,18,FMr Dye said Curtis, who was charged
OL,19,Fwith causing death by dangerous
OL,20,Fdriving in July, had voluntarily
OL,21,Fsurrendered her driving licence.
