OL,7,FIn a statement issued through Dyfed-
OL,8,FPowys Police at the time of her
OL,9,Fcharge, Mabli's family described the
OL,10,Fpast year as "the most horrendous time
OL,11,Fof our lives".
OL,13,FThey said: "Every day is a day of pain
OL,14,Ffor us, even now, but as parents we
OL,15,Fstill have to give the love and
OL,16,Fsupport our other children need as
OL,17,Fthey are still trying to come to terms
OL,18,Fwith losing their baby sister."
