OL,7,FThey thanked police for their work on
OL,8,Fthe case, and the 2Wish charity for
OL,9,Fassisting them as a family.
OL,11,FAn inquest opening in July last year
OL,12,Fheard that Mabli died from severe
OL,13,Ftraumatic brain injuries.
OL,15,FCurtis will next appear before Swansea
OL,16,FCrown Court for sentence on November
OL,17,F22.
